text: Ðis is þara V hida boc æt rimtune þæ Eadred cining gebocode Brihtrice his þegne on ece yrfe.
Ðis synd þa landgemæra To Rimtune.
Ærest on mearh forda upp on hunig broces stream of beorhtulfes ge mær dic.
Ðonon suð on þa dic of ða west langan dic.
Of þære dic on wændan mæres lace.
Æft of mor dic norð on wendan beorges hearpað.
Of þam hearpaðe on wiðig leas wyrtruman ofer cattes flot on eatan beares wyrtruman.
Þonon east oþ oslaces leas eastende norð be wyrttruman on ða eastlangan dicwale.
Þonon east on dic oþ heo wend norð on hig broces stream þonon æft upp andlang streames on mæreforð neoðo weardne.
Þonon norð andlang dic utt þurh wynna wudu on stroð norðwearð.
Þonon east on þone mær hagan.
Andlang hagan suþ on feld on wyrttruman oþ wederan grafes suð ende.
Þonne west andlang hear poðes suð on þa ealdan dic æft on mer forð.
